* Interface to receive callbacks from ITunerResourceManager.
 * 
 * @hide

methods.name: public void onReclaimResources() throws android.os.RemoteException
methods.comment:
* TRM invokes this method when the client's resources need to be reclaimed. * *

This method is implemented in Tuner Framework to take the reclaiming * actions. It's a synchronous call. TRM would wait on the call to finish * then grant the resource.
